\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"4. Disclosure of Your Information\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"We do not sell, trade, rent, or otherwise transfer your personally identifiable information (like name and email) to outside parties for their marketing purposes without your consent. We may share information under the following circumstances:\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-6 space-y-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"By Law or to Protect Rights\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"If we believe the release of information about you is necessary to respond to legal process (e.g., subpoena, court order), to investigate or remedy potential violations of our policies, or to protect the rights, property, and safety of IndoorDogPark, our users, or others, we may share your information as permitted or required by any applicable law, rule, or regulation.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Third-Party Service Providers\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"We may share your information with third-party vendors, service providers, contractors, or agents who perform services for us or on our behalf and require access to such information to do that work. Examples include:\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 ml-6 list-disc space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Data analysis and website analytics (e.g., Google Analytics)\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Email delivery for contact form responses and newsletters\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Hosting services and cloud infrastructure providers\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Payment processing services (e.g., Stripe)\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Map and geolocation services\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"We only share the minimum information necessary for them to perform their designated functions, and we make reasonable efforts to ensure they are obligated to maintain the confidentiality and security of your information.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Advertising Partners\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"As mentioned, we allow third-party advertising partners like Google AdSense to use tracking technologies on the Site. This allows them to collect information about your interaction with our Site and other websites to display relevant advertisements. This information is collected directly by these third parties, and their use of it is governed by their own privacy policies. We do not share your personally identifiable information (like name or email) directly with advertisers.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Specifically, Google and other third-party vendors may place and read cookies on your browser, or use web beacons to collect information, as a result of ad serving on our website. This includes collecting device-specific information (such as device type, operating system, and browser type), IP addresses, and approximate location data to deliver relevant advertisements.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Park Owners or Partners\\\"}],\\\"$L30\\\"]}],\\\"$L31\\\"]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"21:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"article\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/80 p-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"5. Data Security\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"We use administrative, technical, and physical security measures to help protect your personal information. This includes using HTTPS (SSL/TLS) for data transmission between your browser and our Site, and relying on the security practices of our hosting providers and service partners.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"However, please be aware that despite our efforts, no security measures are perfect or impenetrable, and no method of data transmission can be guaranteed against any interception or other type of misuse. Any information disclosed online is vulnerable to interception and misuse by unauthorized parties. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security if you provide personal information.\\\"}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"22:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"article\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"6. Your Data Rights (e.g., GDPR, CCPA)\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Depending on your geographic location and applicable data protection laws, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information. These may include:\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 ml-6 list-disc space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The right to access\\\"}],\\\" – You have the right to request copies of your personal data that we hold\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The right to rectification\\\"}],\\\" – You have the right to request that we correct any information you believe is inaccurate or complete information you believe is incomplete\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The right to erasure (Right to be Forgotten)\\\"}],\\\" – You have the right to request that we erase your personal data that we hold, under certain conditions\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The right to restrict processing\\\"}],\\\" – You have the right to request that we restrict the processing of your personal data, under certain conditions\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The right to object to processing\\\"}],\\\" – You have the right to object to our processing of your personal data, under certain conditions\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The right to data portability\\\"}],\\\" – You have the right to request that we transfer the data that we have collected (that pertains to you) to another organization, or directly to you, under certain conditions\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA), you are covered by the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). If you are a California resident, you are covered by the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) / California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA).\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"To exercise these rights, or to make inquiries about your data, please contact us at \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"a\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"mailto:media@indoordogpark.org\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-violet-600 hover:text-violet-700 underline\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"media@indoordogpark.org\\\"}],\\\". We respond within 30 days unless additional verification is required. For managing advertising preferences related to cookies, please refer to the \\\\\\\"Cookies and Tracking Technologies\\\\\\\" section and the opt-out links provided.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"We do not \\\\\\\"sell\\\\\\\" your personal information in the traditional sense of exchanging it for monetary compensation. However, the use of advertising cookies by third parties like Google AdSense for personalized advertising may be considered a \\\\\\\"sale\\\\\\\" or \\\\\\\"sharing\\\\\\\" under laws like the CCPA/CPRA. You can opt-out of such personalized advertising as described in the \\\\\\\"Cookies and Tracking Technologies\\\\\\\" section.\\\"}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"23:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"article\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/80 p-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"7. Children's Privacy\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Our Site and Services are not directed to, and we do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from, children under the age of 13 (or a higher age threshold as required by applicable law, e.g., 16 in certain EEA jurisdict